metadata.name: The Pool of Life
metadata.description: Rumors floated around the globe of a mysterious well filled with water. Water known to contain the power to keep one's beauty, one's health, one's age, even. At least, that's what the general consensus was. None had seen it in person, and those that had suffered a fate worse than death. In hearing the news of the water's sudden rise in popularity, Heaven sent an angel down to earth. "Keep the people safe! This water must not reach their tongues!"
